title: Jean Michel Jarre - Concerts in China 1981 - Australian DVD
description:
JEAN MICHEL JARRE - Concerts in China 1981.

DVD from the famous Chinese concerts Jean Michel Jarre did in China in 1981.
He was the first western musician performing Live in China.

This is the first release of the concert on DVD.

Audio: Dolby AC3 48000Hz 6ch 192Kbps [AC-3]
Video: MPEG2 Video 720x576 (4:3) 25.00fps 9800Kbps [Video]
No CSS.

FULL DVD including Cover and DVD print.

This is not a bootleg VHS RIP. This is taken from the Australian release DVD.
